Package: ZEUS
Title: Analyze ZEUS Electrophysiology Stimulus-Response Recordings
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Logan", "Ouellette", email = "lo2252@users.noreply.github.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Logan Ouellette [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Logan Ouellette <lo2252@users.noreply.github.com>
Description: Imports ABF electrophysiology recordings, applies ZEUS C0 and C1
    stimulus-response protocol metadata, computes averaged ERG traces and
    peak statistics, and exports validation-ready summaries for downstream
    analysis.
